data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING 10K CREDIT upon successful closing towards approved lenders closing costs, rate buy downs or carpet. Amazing home in 83709! Proximity to shopping, freeway access and more! Beautiful open floorplan featuring great room with vaulted ceilings and cozy gas fireplace. Kitchen with large breakfast bar, granite tile counters, stainless appliances, gas cooktop, pantry and more. Formal dining space on the main could serve as formal office space. Main level primary suite with dual vanities, separate tub and shower and walk in closet. Large fully fenced yard with 2 included sheds, mature landscaping and covered back patio. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
